#

Quick Borscht with Canned Beets

30 min
$10
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Soup

Tags:

QuickHealthyComfort Food

Description

A vibrant and hearty beet soup, perfect for a quick, nutritious meal.

Ingredients

  • canned beets: 2 cups
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • potato, diced: 1 medium
  • carrot, grated: 1 large
  • onion, chopped: 1 small
  • cabbage, shredded: 2 cups
  • sour cream: 1/2 cup
  • fresh dill, chopped: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
